{"tid":2032960,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"執法者的事，能算偷麼？","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T11:36:51.000Z","uid":156509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fed2ca236861ac59a1754de78dd4f9205b9c2958","tid":2032960,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又偷了人家的東西了！」牙蛇睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我今天親眼見你偷了ok的水，拍埋片。」牙蛇便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「借水不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;偷水！&hellip;&hellip;執法者的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「事後比返」，什麼「法律」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"10b9ac21f9649abf04ac460c1c8a05bb9d391701","tid":2032960,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"香港法律有幾多種寫法？"},{"pid":"1618d01843508a27f8c0c485d2830a0a7db17f81","tid":2032960,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"黑警快D自殺死"},{"pid":"84da1449bf600ef30f0ffce13afec11e70790a47","tid":2032960,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1618d01843508a27f8c0c485d2830a0a7db17f81","tid":2032960,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"黑警快D自殺死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iK28FmT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiK28FmT.gif&h=c1fc851b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}